Design Systems

NSW Government has a centrally maintained open-to-everyone design system, and additional GELs and component libraries are available in several departments.

NSW brand framework

NSW Government branding applies to all government entities, with rules for those who use the waratah logo and those who are co-brand, standalone, or independent.

Follow the branding rules at all times, even if you're not using a pre-made design system or GEL.

Primary Design Systems

NSW Design System

Use the NSW Design System as a brand-compliant foundation for your own component library, or with its pre-made components.

Available as: Figma, Framer, HTML & CSS, React, Next.js

east
Service NSW GEL

Use the Service NSW to build transactions hosted on service.nsw.gov.au. (login required)

Available as: Figma, Sketch, React
